              <div data-w-tab="Description" class="integration-tab w-tab-pane w--tab-active">
                <div class="rich-text w-richtext">
                  <p>
                    <strong>X Bot</strong> is an innovative Telegram solution by BWS that empowers community groups to monitor
                    and enhance their engagement on X (formerly Twitter) through a gamified experience. By allowing group
                    admins to set up custom monitoring filters based on specific X accounts, keywords, or mentions, X Bot
                    fetches relevant public posts using the X API and compiles leaderboard reports that highlight the most
                    active and supportive community members.​
                  </p>
                  <h4><strong>Features</strong></h4>
                  <h5><strong>Custom Monitoring Filters</strong></h5>
                  <p>
                    <strong>‍</strong>X Bot enables group admins to configure filters tailored to their community&#x27;s
                    interests. Whether tracking specific X accounts, keywords, or mentions, the bot ensures that only
                    relevant content is monitored, providing a focused engagement experience.​
                  </p>
                  <h5><strong>Real-Time Data Fetching</strong>‍</h5>
                  <p>
                    Leveraging the X API, X Bot retrieves pertinent public posts in real-time, ensuring that community
                    interactions are based on the most current information available.​
                  </p>
                  <h5><strong>Gamified Leaderboards</strong>‍</h5>
                  <p>
                    To foster a competitive and engaging environment, X Bot compiles leaderboard reports that showcase
                    the most active and supportive community members. This gamified approach incentivizes participation
                    and recognizes top contributors.​
                  </p>
                  <h4><strong>Benefits</strong></h4>
                  <h5><strong>Enhanced Community Engagement</strong>‍</h5>
                  <p>
                    By spotlighting active members and encouraging participation through leaderboards, X Bot cultivates
                    a more engaged and vibrant community atmosphere.​
                  </p>
                  <h5><strong>Tailored Content Monitoring</strong></h5>
                  <p>
                    <strong>‍</strong>The customizable filters ensure that communities can focus on specific topics or
                    accounts, making the engagement more relevant and meaningful.​
                  </p>
                  <h5><strong>Data-Driven Insights</strong>‍</h5>
                  <p>
                    With data fetching and reporting, community admins gain valuable insights into member activities and
                    engagement trends, facilitating informed decision-making.​
                  </p>
                  <p>‍</p>
                  <p>
                    Join the growing number of communities leveraging X Bot to transform their engagement strategies on
                    X. Experience a more interactive and rewarding community journey today!​
                  </p>
                  <p>‍</p>
                </div>
